summary: This give you all the daedric weapons and armour.
descriptionHtml:
This give you:
- Daedric Boots
- Daedric Armor
- Daedric Gauntlets
- Daedric Helmet
- Daedric Shield
- Daedric War Axe
- Daedric Battleaxe
- Daedric Bow
- Daedric Dagger
- Daedric Greatsword
- Daedric Mace
- Daedric Sword
- Daedric Warhammer
- Daedric Arrow (x100)

[color=#FFFF00]Installation:[/color]

- Drag the file to your Skyrim Folder.

[color=#FFFF00]Uninstall:[/color]

- Just delete the file.

[color=#FFFF00]How To Use:[/color]

- Load your game and open the console, then type: bat alldaedric
